0035|#FRAMES=<list_of_frame_specifications>
S   |        <                            >
0036|*gives a list of extra frames (boxes) to be drawn in the current graph.
0037|*Each member of this list is a word (name of the frame) and any such
0038|*a frame must be given in the form
0040|*   <name_of_the_frame>=<xhome>,<yhome>,<width>,<height>,<fill>
S   |    <                 > <     > <     > <     > <      > <    >
0042|*where (xhome,yhome) are the coordinates of the left-bottom corner of
0043|*the frame and <width> and <height> give the size of of the frame. All
S   |               <     >     <      >
0044|*the values are in plotting units (not in user coordinates).
0045|*<fill> is optional and gives the fill index. The default is no fill.
S   | <    >
