0128|*(in the PLOT /FRAME operation)
0129|*gives a list of extra sequences of line segments to be drawn in the
0130|*current graph. Each member of this list is a word (name of the
0131|*sequence) and any such a sequence must be given in the form
0133|*   <name_of_the_sequence>=xhome,yhome,x1,y1,x2,y2,...,xn,yn
