0135|*Then a polyline starting from point (xhome,yhome) and going through
0136|*points
0137|*        (xhome+x1,xhome+y1)
0138|*        (xhome+x1+x2,yhome+y1,y2)
0139|*        ...
0140|*        (xhome+x1+x2+...+xn,yhome+y1+y2+...+yn)
0141|*will be drawn.
0142|*All the values are in plotting units (not in user coordinates).
